values:
Vestiphobia: Fear of clothing.
Porphyrophobia: Fear of the color purple.
Aulophobia: Fear of flutes. 
Paraskavedekatriaphobia: Fear of Friday the 13th.
Dextrophobia: Fear of objects at the right side of the body. 
Hierophobia: Fear of priests or sacred things.
Papaphobia: Fear of the Pope.
Chronemophobia: Fear of thinking. 
Euphobia: Fear of hearing good news
Thaasophobia: Fear of sitting.
Mnemophobia: Fear of memories. 
Pentheraphobia: Fear of mother-in-laws

Just an update guys, in case you might be wondering- I'm turning 16 in six days. 







yay!
This is just a journal for my friends' list; I don't post here anymore. And yes- unconscious is spelled wrong.
